'''MapR'''是一所美国企业管理软件公司、全球三大Hadoop开源大数据软件的提供商之一，总部位于[[美国|美国]][[加州|加州]][[圣何塞市|圣何塞市]]，主要参与大数据的安全优化与开发、销售[[Apache_Hadoop|Apache Hadoop]]的衍生软件。MapR和[[Apache_Hadoop|Apache Hadoop]]一起参加过[[Apache_HBase|HBase]]、[[Apache_Hive|Apache Hive]]、[[Apache_ZooKeeper|Apache ZooKeeper]]等项目的研发。MAPR曾被亚马逊云服务选择为[[亞馬遜公司|亚马逊]]弹性云EC2的升级版本。<ref name="emr-mapr">{{Cite web|url=http://aws.amazon.com/elasticmapreduce/mapr/|title=Amazon EMR with the MapR Distribution for Hadoop|accessdate=25 June 2011|archive-date=2012-06-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120616033124/http://aws.amazon.com/elasticmapreduce/mapr/}}</ref><ref name="emr-announce">{{Cite web|url=http://gigaom.com/cloud/amazon-taps-mapr-for-high-powered-elastic-mapreduce/|title=Amazon Taps MapR for High Powered Elastic Map Reduce|accessdate=25 June 2011|archive-date=2012-11-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121106124833/http://gigaom.com/cloud/amazon-taps-mapr-for-high-powered-elastic-mapreduce/}}</ref>MapR称，目前为止该公司的付费认证客户总数已达500家。<span class="cx-segment" data-segmentid="66"></span>

MapR的大部分高管都来自Google、Lightspeed Venture Partners、Informatica、[[EMC|EMC]]和Veoh。

2011年8月，MapR开展了第二轮融资。<ref name="redpoint">{{Cite web|url=http://www.cnbc.com/id/44325254/MapR_Technologies_Secures_20_Million_in_Funding_Investment_to_Fuel_Rapid_Adoption_for_Big_Data_Analytics_and_Hadoop|title=MapR Technologies Secures 20 million in Funding|accessdate=19 Sep 2011}}</ref><ref name="nyt-redpoint">{{Cite web|url=http://www.nytimes.com/external/venturebeat/2011/08/30/30venturebeat-mapr-makes-friends-of-hadoop-and-the-enterpr-34892.html|title=MapR Makes Friends of Hadoop|accessdate=19 Sep 2011}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://allthingsd.com/20130318/mapr-lands-30-million-series-c-led-by-mayfield-fund/|title=MapR Lands $30 Million Series C Led by Mayfield Fund.|accessdate=9 May 2013|last=Hesseldahl|first=Arik|publisher=All Things D|archive-date=2013-05-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130505051858/http://allthingsd.com/20130318/mapr-lands-30-million-series-c-led-by-mayfield-fund/}}</ref>

